{"tid":608852,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"做緊/讀緊/有興趣做社工嘅入嚟放低心事啦","createTime":"2018-03-28T13:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T06:59:06.000Z","uid":61910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a6031ba30ef5511db2f9a23c66cf186f8f28e2c4","tid":608852,"uid":61910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T13:40:16.000Z","msg":"無論你係在學/在職/已死嘅社工都歡迎入嚟傾下計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係社工嘅對呢行有興趣/想八掛下嘅又可以一齊吹下水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外呢度有個TG谷歡迎在職社工加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地希望透過彼此侃侃而談，從而增加各位對實務工作能力。<br />\n亦歡迎大家提供各類同輩支援，職場和機構交流的資訊！<br />\n<br />\n想加入就填咗下面張form啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1_SX8hflQzISx4OW2hyrE_1MK8PdVdphY6UuZFNH6ifA/viewform?edit_requested=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F1_SX8hflQzISx4OW2hyrE_1MK8PdVdphY6UuZFNH6ifA%2Fviewform%3Fedit_requested%3Dtrue&d=PiMb9u8Td%2BQ%2BW%2B9fe70%2FsjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=e25e1c86\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1_SX8hflQzISx4OW2hyrE_1MK8PdVdphY6UuZFNH6ifA/viewform?edit_requested=true</a>"},{"pid":"b2d86a6246dfb5b1fa080704b8a1fd082a360e03","tid":608852,"uid":61910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T13:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae324d30c139adbbbbf7bedfbf79c62bfb81d5e","tid":608852,"uid":61910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T13:59:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b1d3b561a3a91adb717a714c5c4f7daf853acf","tid":608852,"uid":85979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T15:39:23.000Z","msg":"咁有心開個谷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2d2ab23a0e2e065268ebce1657a5d372284f67","tid":608852,"uid":10221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T16:10:50.000Z","msg":"未入行讀緊書 但係見到前景灰灰地 就算幾有抱負同理想 係而家社會服務環境 又要追數又勁多paper 慢慢都會磨滅曬個種火 好怕自己第時burn out得好快 仲要好多NGO肥上瘦下得好嚴重 見到啲front line 做到死咁 人工都係唔足point 真係對將來幾頹下"},{"pid":"005cef78fdb9d32ae93423614a5bf3d472d2ce06","tid":608852,"uid":157894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T18:41:45.000Z","msg":"對於前景真係唔樂觀<br />\n因為變晒質<br />\n為服務而做服務<br />\n唔係為左client而做服務<br />\n<br />\n又好難做一d倡導既工作<br />\n因為機構怕左政府"},{"pid":"4f10e542ca86da7612d1166d0017dc81f97bcc3c","tid":608852,"uid":61341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T20:02:34.000Z","msg":"讀緊社工 覺得能醫但不自醫咁<br />\n自己近排壓力好大 成日情緒低落<br />\n連學都冇翻咁濟 就黎又final <br />\n今個sem應該食得屎"},{"pid":"c7e4babfcb7768fcebb96f17fd6a8462f08668e7","tid":608852,"uid":140590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T20:06:48.000Z","msg":"想讀社工"},{"pid":"ad41c987a478ef9ca094abb9b561df3f74c1254e","tid":608852,"uid":61910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T01:25:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未入行讀緊書 但係見到前景灰灰地 就算幾有抱負同理想 係而家社會服務環境 又要追數又勁多paper 慢慢都會磨滅曬個種火 好怕自己第時burn out得好快 仲要好多NGO肥上瘦下得好嚴重 見到啲front line 做到死咁 人工都係唔足point 真係對將來幾頹下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只能講呢行叫比上不足比下有餘<br />\n龍頭個幾檔都足point嘅但mid-point封頂<br />\n今時今日叫做起薪唔錯長遠一般啦<br />\n<br />\n至於Burnout問題<br />\n我只能講<br />\n期望越大 失望越大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過好在呢行叫可以轉下field<br />\n或者去到新嘅環境會有新體驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b7e12073a8d78b5f440dcc575dd87c3b79c462d","tid":608852,"uid":61910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T01:31:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對於前景真係唔樂觀<br />\n因為變晒質<br />\n為服務而做服務<br />\n唔係為左client而做服務<br />\n<br />\n又好難做一d倡導既工作<br />\n因為機構怕左政府</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好話做倡導工作<br />\n連社區性嘅工作都越來越少人肯做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個個讀書讀counselling/乜乜物物therapy<br />\n仲有幾多人肯拋個身出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過最近多新邨入伙多返人講屋邨社工隊<br />\n但日曬雨淋有時甚至連中心都唔固定個時<br />\n又真係好難吸引到人做"},{"pid":"151b2d106927e7b8b355d1189b39b277ed2167f6","tid":608852,"uid":44647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T01:49:39.000Z","msg":"而家呢個年代好多野都已經fix 死哂<br />\n你想做得好或者做D 新少少既野阻力會好大<br />\n<br />\n亦都會加倍地辛苦<br />\n<br />\n我就建議每個FG 應該試下既<br />\n始終你後生唔瘋狂一下<br />\n到你做返十年八年<br />\n你就會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我到而家都係覺得社工係一份幾好玩既職業黎<br />\n大家俾心機努力下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f71cf78da693a3d12f18c40c19fa44bb002d8b","tid":608852,"uid":61910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T01:57:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家呢個年代好多野都已經fix 死哂<br />\n你想做得好或者做D 新少少既野阻力會好大<br />\n<br />\n亦都會加倍地辛苦<br />\n<br />\n我就建議每個FG 應該試下既<br />\n始終你後生唔瘋狂一下<br />\n到你做返十年八年<br />\n你就會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我到而家都係覺得社工係一份幾好玩既職業黎<br />\n大家俾心機努力下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過首先你要有個好老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個肯比你做比你試<br />\n同一個死咕咕嘅老闆真係可以有好大分別"},{"pid":"d62d6ee9b538831f2761e2db47bfd23429b32505","tid":608852,"uid":57255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T18:25:44.000Z","msg":"已apply<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee1676be02fb95f12636d5966019c8e891cd65c","tid":608852,"uid":116131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T18:29:41.000Z","msg":"想讀pt degree <br />\n但得番明愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n想繼續進修，full time又只睇成績，可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a305900a4cc9f911cd0a2b6764f6a13c311b5f3","tid":608852,"uid":172472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T18:40:48.000Z","msg":"擔心讀完搵唔到工<br />\n<br />\n今年9年讀浸大msw<br />\n之前都做開HR<br />\n想轉行"},{"pid":"b2a7ed2e8ff6b7e711d81b22cc9840851ec5877b","tid":608852,"uid":57255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ee1676be02fb95f12636d5966019c8e891cd65c","tid":608852,"uid":116131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T18:29:41.000Z","msg":"想讀pt degree <br />\n但得番明愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n想繼續進修，full time又只睇成績，可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T00:27:05.000Z","msg":"poly都唔開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"c836067107cf0ef0afd91eee501b8fbfefc7be62","tid":608852,"uid":116131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2a7ed2e8ff6b7e711d81b22cc9840851ec5877b","tid":608852,"uid":57255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ee1676be02fb95f12636d5966019c8e891cd65c","tid":608852,"uid":116131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T18:29:41.000Z","msg":"想讀pt degree <br />\n但得番明愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n想繼續進修，full time又只睇成績，可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T00:27:05.000Z","msg":"poly都唔開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:58:19.000Z","msg":"無肉食，收哂檔喇"},{"pid":"577621f6894590730531a2a5856674a4b7243a17","tid":608852,"uid":113675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T10:10:19.000Z","msg":"未畢業<br />\n<br />\n但實習老細暗示俾位我 (有機會A仔位)<br />\n<br />\